@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001/api

### 1) Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "email": "alex@quizquest.com",
  "password": "1234"
}

### 2) Register
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "New Player",
  "email": "newplayer@quizquest.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 3) Forgot Password (simulado)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "email": "alex@quizquest.com"
}

### Copia el token de login/register y pegalo aqui:
@authToken = REEMPLAZAR_TOKEN

### 4) Obtener usuario autenticado actual
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### 5) Obtener perfil de usuario por ID (mismo usuario del token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### 6) Obtener todas las asignaturas con progreso del usuario autenticado
GET {{baseUrl}}/subjects
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### 7) Guardar resultado de quiz (actualiza XP)
POST {{baseUrl}}/quiz/finish
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "subjectId": "josemaria_zaragoza_1920_1927",
  "score": 90,
  "xpEarned": 45
}

### 8) Logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json
